To build: configure nginx like this

configure --add-module=/path/to/this/directory ...other..flags...

also install openvcdiff packages

Configuration: on the location level

sdch on/off -- enable/disable (default: disable)

sdch_dict <filename> .... -- files with the dictionaries. Mandatory if enabled

sdch_url <url> -- url to suggest the client if it does not have the
  dictionary. Mandatory if enabled. Variables allowed.

sdch_maxnoadv <num>. Optional, default: 1. 
  Suppress Get-Dictionary advertisements if the client's dictionary is in
  the beginning of the sdch_dict list (up to the given number).

  Example.
    sdch_dict /dict/1 /dict/2 /dict/3
    sdch_url http://server/dict/1
    sdch_maxnoadv 2
    Hashes:
      /dict/1         abcdefgh
      /dict/2         zyxwvuts
      /dict/3         01234567

    Client:
      Avail-Dictionary: abcdefgh
    Server:
      doesn't send Get-Dictionary 

   Client:
     Avail-Dictionary: zyxwvuts
   Server:
     doesn't send Get-Dictionary

   Client:
     Avail-Dictionary: 01234567
   Server:
     Get-Dictionary: http://server/dict/1

   Client:
     no Avail-Dictionary
   Server:
     Get-Dictionary: http://server/dict/1

sdch_disablecv <expr> -- optional. Disable SDCH if the value is non-empty
  and is not equal to 0.

